title: The Honeymooners - The Lost Episodes 1952-55
description:
This is the first (of 3) parts with the classic 1950&#039;s Honeymooners. Starring Jackie Gleason, Art Carney, Audrey Meadows and Joyce Randolph

These episodes have been collected in the order of their transmission date as far as possible. The original &#039;Lost episodes&#039; DVDs were in awful shape and I&#039;ve tried to do the best possible from them. Here is all the episodes from &#039;The Jackie Gleason show&#039; 1952-1955

In 1955 The Honeymooners became a show of it&#039;s own and that will be last part I upload. The last &#039;Lost episodes&#039; from 1956-1957 as well as all the special features and undated episodes from all the &#039;Lost episodes&#039; DVDs will make out the second part.

As for seeding: I will try to seed 100% 24/7 until each part is available, but my ISP have it&#039;s glitches and I&#039;ll only be able to fix it during evenings CET. My upload speed should be about 768kbit/s assuming everything is OK. I&#039;ll upload the next part as soon as possible.
